# The Luxe Bureau Landing Page - Development Rules

## Project Overview
Building a pixel-perfect, responsive luxury landing page for The Luxe Bureau using HTML, Tailwind CSS v4, and vanilla JavaScript. Focus on elegant typography, smooth animations, and premium aesthetics.

## Typography System

### Font Loading Strategy
- Use Google Fonts with appropriate fallbacks
- Primary fonts: SchoolBook (fallback: serif), Century Old Style Std (fallback: serif), Quadrant Text (fallback: sans-serif), ABC Marfa (fallback: sans-serif)
- Implement font-display: swap for performance
- Use system font stack as ultimate fallback

### Typography Specifications
```css
/* SchoolBook variants */
.font-schoolbook {
  font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif; /* Google Fonts alternative */
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 5%;
  line-height: 100%;
}

/* Century Old Style Std variants */
.font-century {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; /* Google Fonts alternative */
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 2%;
  line-height: 40px;
}

/* Quadrant Text variants */
.font-quadrant {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; /* Google Fonts alternative */
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0%;
}

/* ABC Marfa variants */
.font-abc-marfa {
  font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; /* Google Fonts alternative */
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 10%;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
```

