## Responsive Design Strategy

### Breakpoint Usage
- Mobile-first approach using Tailwind's default breakpoints
- sm: 640px, md: 768px, lg: 1024px, xl: 1280px, 2xl: 1536px
- Ensure seamless scaling from mobile (320px) to desktop (1920px+)

### Component Responsive Patterns
- Hero section: Stack vertically on mobile, horizontal layout on lg+
- Bento grid: Single column on mobile, 2 cols on md, 4 cols on lg+
- Typography: Scale font sizes proportionally across breakpoints
- Carousel: Touch-friendly on mobile, hover states on desktop

